Like all other girls, Ariel and Barbie also want to live a life of super hero. Their unique dream has forced us to come up with a brand new dressing game of girls where these two pretties are ready to become a super hero. Your objective in Disney Super Princess 1 game is to help them to realize their dream. No, you do not have to put extra efforts to do so. You see your princesses standing on the left side of the screen and the right side of the screen will show you outfit and accessory options.
